                                       2. ALGORITHM 
Step 1: Start the Game 
Set state = MENU 
Set wave = 1 
Set money = 100 
Set baseHealth = 5 
Set baseEnemyHealth = 30 
Set towerCount = 0 
Create arrays: 
Towers[MAX_TOWERS] 
enemies[MAX_ENEMIES] 
Step 2: Display Menu 
Display game title and instructions 
Wait for user to press Enter 
Change game state to PLAYING 
Step 3: Game Loop (Repeat until state = GAME_OVER) 
Step 4: Render Game Status 
Step 5: Display- 
Current wave number 
Available money 
Base health 
Step 6: Tower Placement 
If towerCount < MAX_TOWERS:
Display tower options:Set state = GAME_OVER 
Else: 
Increase wave number by 1 
Step 7: End Game 
Display "GAME OVER" 
Display final wave reached
Step 8: Stop 
